{"tid":1217330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump回應香港遊行： 係我見過最大型嘅示威","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T22:08:36.000Z","uid":86402,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8191cb7c643878f81d4f8cc94d530a4add09f419","tid":1217330,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"Trump回應記者提問時表示，香港遊行係我見過最大型嘅示威，佢地話有一百萬人，有時有d人會報大數，但我睇過絕對有一百萬。"},{"pid":"0cfa7dfe98911d9b4621aaf3fa963a5e333a801f","tid":1217330,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"From有線新聞"},{"pid":"59165a137281647640e13e629931df738977a8ed","tid":1217330,"uid":100550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救 <br />\n今次呢件事 會令到我地香港人更團結<br />\n更融洽"},{"pid":"e7260e2412a11090decb9b9e542ccccd67d42448","tid":1217330,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"比侵侵睇下班警犬全部都係冇良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下為集眾人之力結合成嘅圖集，希望大家可以幫手廣傳：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2299277576830901%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=1b118f55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/</a><br />\n<br />\n612嗰日一位16歲女學生嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議大家可以聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完之後我好嬲，亦都好想喊，香港今時今日嘅景況，除咗班高官之外，班蓄生警犬亦都有份一手一腳造成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映：</span></span><br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c1bf84f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=832dbd4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c5ecb5b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=be33ef3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=a8e65ddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=f38ffbcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n事後嚟張大合照慶功先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BUJgDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BUJgDg.png&h=d811719e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議告上聯合國！向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},{"pid":"2491f524f5cff303f111a